{"tid":1492324,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我地有手足俾公安捉左，唔係當冇事發生下話？","createTime":"2019-08-20T19:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T20:31:23.000Z","uid":265956,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9d4372d51c86cf2dd6d2fdb054a94affea9e92cc","tid":1492324,"uid":265956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T19:15:41.000Z","msg":"英領館港職員自深圳返港途中疑被扣　英外交部表關注 (16:22)<br />\n<br />\n一名在英國駐香港領事館工作的港人職員早前從深圳回港時，疑遭內地當局被拘留。英國外交部回應稱，關注有關事件，正向廣東省與香港當局索取進一步資料，並向被扣職員的家屬提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》今日（20日）報道，疑被拘的是28歲Simon Cheng，為英國駐香港總領事館蘇格蘭國際發展局員工，本月8日於深圳搭乘高鐵回港，當時通知女友正在過境，但其後失聯，至今已超過10日。Simon的女友及家人懷疑Simon被內地當局拘留，其女友根據Simon的短訊，估計Simon可能於西九龍站內地口岸被拘留。<br />\n<br />\n英國外交部發言人今日回應稱，「關注有同事從深圳返港被扣留的報道」，正向其家人提供援助，並向粵港當局尋求更多資料。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，Simon 既屋企人都有回應同解釋情況<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/114456586582381/posts/114883506539689?s=1409273133&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F114456586582381%2Fposts%2F114883506539689%3Fs%3D1409273133%26sfns%3Dmo&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41P%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=29b4ad41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/114456586582381/posts/114883506539689?s=1409273133&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有手足俾人捉左啊！大家做嘢啦！<br />\n<br />\n聽日係英領會有個聲援Simon 既集會！希望到時會見到大家！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n緊急抗議 - 救救 Simon Cheng - 一位在英國駐港總領事館工作的香港人<br />\n<br />\n地點：英國駐港總領事館 (金鐘)<br />\n日期： 2019年8月21日<br />\n時間：下午五時至傍晚七時"},{"pid":"918218989ad9e8a223e5a99e82c65a8100c7acc9","tid":1492324,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T19:16:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2c70ff35a4c10eea7ba5769f04fc44a5017b135e","tid":1492324,"uid":265956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T19:16:22.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"84447caa84849301e4db8469f9e3dcb2a59de103","tid":1492324,"uid":265956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T19:16:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4dd4219c190a32e053d716e87cf724bb970f522","tid":1492324,"uid":7081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T19:17:05.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"21e739e4752d71da194807518e4c2d3c42338fb8","tid":1492324,"uid":58732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T19:17:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8ccaa24925efd9f66386645dca0f61cbc9f6777f","tid":1492324,"uid":266314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T19:20:52.000Z","msg":"香港人加油"},{"pid":"0cbecca5aedf585cc5134ebe692ed4d637f90438","tid":1492324,"uid":276495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T19:21:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"20c755c032dbc4b3c4cb0e5ca86ce571d2114604","tid":1492324,"uid":122593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T19:22:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"57647d0702273bb14689549e5ff6bd3be0d4a1e0","tid":1492324,"uid":265956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T19:24:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c82c622e127346cee457869cf0cfb22f5292c39e","tid":1492324,"uid":265956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T19:25:31.000Z","msg":"P牌講嘢冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd02e671b40010fafd710a9d2bb111d98cc9468f","tid":1492324,"uid":88300,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T19:25:37.000Z","msg":"英國駐港領事館職員<br />\n<br />\n唔好講咩手足<br />\n佢個職業係國際問題"},{"pid":"6cb8f2647416b43458f7f619b04e41e06375f7e8","tid":1492324,"uid":265956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T19:45:57.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"aae21fe63db09aff06482e4ce94c342855d6d3e3","tid":1492324,"uid":183344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T20:19:13.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"4d90004eb3e0befa14f7d724a781b8440e282ace","tid":1492324,"uid":50253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T20:24:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你自己香港手足都救唔撚到<br />\n點救地獄鬼國既手足呀"},{"pid":"26fc95625133c52263a0a680eae5f466d9970fda","tid":1492324,"uid":5489,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T20:25:42.000Z","msg":"佢係英國外交部既issue<br />\n你屈人做義士只會更難救人"},{"pid":"05f1bc0b37cdac5feec3392f9ce94e33c95975ba","tid":1492324,"uid":207259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T20:31:23.000Z","msg":"超過10日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}